'Aditya, terima kasih.'

00:20:47.240 --> 00:20:48.280 line:20%
'Kamu menyelamatkan kami.'

00:20:48.360 --> 00:20:50.920 line:20%
'Tolong hentikan drama ini!'

00:20:55.280 --> 00:20:56.600 line:20%
'Jadi, kecurigaanku benar.'

00:20:56.640 --> 00:20:59.600 line:20%
'Kamu sangat menjijikkan, Mahima!  Bagaimana
kamu bisa membungkuk begitu rendah!'

00:21:00.960 --> 00:21:01.920 line:20%
'Karun!'

00:21:02.640 --> 00:21:04.040 line:20%
'Di mana Karun?
